Class HoconSettingsSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saicone.settings.source.HoconSettingsSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SettingsSource
    public class HoconSettingsSource
extends Object
implements SettingsSource
    A settings source for hocon-formatted data
    This class uses lightbend config library to read and write any data.
